This playbook configures new compute node for the cluster.

Before running this playbook you must:
	- Add MAC Address and Hostname to /etc/dnsmasq.conf (Needed for PXE_boot)
	- Add Hostname and IP Address to /etc/ansible/hosts (Needed for PXE_boot)
	- Add root Public Key to new host (Done by Kickstart)
	- Add Hostname to /etc/ansible/hosts
	- Add Hostname to /etc/slurm/slurm.conf

Note: It better to first run the update playbook or update the kernel manually

Option:
	Save the new nodes in 'hosts' and run:
	# ansible-playbook -i hosts new_node.yml 
